

# Join Heather’s Tribe: Grief & Healing Support Circle

## Find Your Community, Heal Together

Welcome to Heather’s Tribe, a compassionate online community where you can navigate grief, share your story, and grow as a Wounded Warrior. Led by Heather Moyer, a certified grief educator and transformational coach based in Mt. Shasta, California, our weekly Grief & Healing Support Circle offers a safe space to connect, heal, and thrive. Grief brings new challenges every day, but you don’t have to face them alone. Through live Zoom meet-ups and Yoga for Grief sessions, Heather’s Tribe provides consistent support, practical tools, and a nurturing community open to all—wherever you are in the world.

