## Why Join Heather’s Tribe?

Grief can feel isolating, but Heather’s Tribe reminds you that you’re never alone. Heather Moyer, a third-generation Mt. Shasta native with over 10 years in wellness, brings her personal experience and professional expertise to every session. After transforming her own life from rock bottom and navigating profound loss, she’s dedicated to helping you find balance and hope. Her mission is to make mental, emotional, and physical well-being accessible, using holistic tools like mindfulness and yoga to empower you as a Wounded Warrior.

